{"tid":880521,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"冇左牙朗蝗馬真係成盤散沙咁","createTime":"2018-10-28T18:14:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-28T18:36:28.000Z","uid":37476,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1ae15a797a881c6de026bc3b4d18ed9da3f963d3","tid":880521,"uid":37476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T18:14:31.000Z","msg":"冇左個主力姐<br />\n當你班前鋒冇左牙朗未習慣組織唔到攻勢<br />\n但班後防做緊啲乜 食撚左屎黎？<br />\n輸巴塞5-1都算 講緊係對啲垃圾隊都係咁俾人入波<br />\n平時拉狗唔係好威又踢人又省人架咩<br />\n冇左牙朗笠曬水？<br />\n人地係祖記發光發熱<br />\n你班友就完全唔知踢緊乜<br />\n再係咁低迷真係下年西乙見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知拿華斯見到25仔失左5球會點諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fb799f87b6b9f253b261279953ace112d8dbd94","tid":880521,"uid":37476,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T18:18:14.000Z","msg":"利申唔係黎引戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9269688752df2184bffe9be366162badb7b71179","tid":880521,"uid":33527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T18:19:50.000Z","msg":"讓因為無撚埋個教練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0420b16aad0f3c2c5ebcbc9e1d406832b8bd852b","tid":880521,"uid":204475,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T18:19:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vaZgCfi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvaZgCfi.gif&h=c7570073&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db4f9c23e8bc634478f55f064b133b9fd81ed93f","tid":880521,"uid":186784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T18:20:52.000Z","msg":"平時朗係到 會成日屌鳩班後防 一失波就會屌醒佢地 再拍手叫佢地專注d 最重要係朗係到對面唔敢谷太上怕比空位牙朗"},{"pid":"30444bdda2ecb91059ca0e383660e754d8aa8d04","tid":880521,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db4f9c23e8bc634478f55f064b133b9fd81ed93f","tid":880521,"uid":186784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T18:20:52.000Z","msg":"平